      "content": "but that's just more work. more talking, more \"processing,\" more trying to navigate a world that feels like it's just waiting for me to trip up again. every time someone tells me \"it gets better\" or to \"seek help,\" it just feels like they're asking me to keep fighting a war that was lost a long time ago. i'm just so tired of the struggle. sometimes i look at the silence and think how much easier it would just be to not have to deal with any of this at all. to just... finally be at rest.",
